    dc:description "Figure 3. Travisia chinensis Grube, 1866 (holotype, ZMB 0629) A complete specimen in lateral view B anterior part in lateral view C posterior part in lateral view. Abbreviations: pr, prostomium; nuO, nuchal organ; mo, mouth; br, branchiae; chaet, chaetiger; IntP, interramal papilla; Pl, parapodia lateral lappet; np, nephridial pores; Py, pygidium." ;
